Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办 该怎么办...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,逃跑是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 妳应该也听不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是怪物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 都叫妳别跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂奥娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那群家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 被牠们逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,牠们...是怪物对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,贝尔 贝尔
